tags.name: Columbia Hills State Park Boat Launch

tags.description: Flat, shallow section of shore, suitable for small personal watercraft put-in and egress. Short portage from parking lot.
tags.note: Formerly mapped as slipway, but there are no man-made features present, just natural shore.
